node.text:
The World’s deepest pool, with a depth of 60 meters (196 feet)! 🤿 Share your photos with us and we will post them in our account. Apply for a feature following the link in our bio: @viewfervor

Who’d you like to swim here with?

📽 @faz3
📍Dubai, UAE

Dreaming of Maldives 💙 We can post your photos in our account, follow the link in our bio: @viewfervor and we will select your pictures

Tag someone you'd visit with! 🇲🇻 

1-5, 7. @giacomo_maldives 
6. @saaidh_7

Hey little guy! @animaledventures show us the pouch, that acts as a warm, safe place for joeys. 🙏🏽 vo1

At around six months, when a baby kangaroo is sufficiently well developed, it will leave the pouch for short periods, returning when it needs to feed. Did you know that?

📽 @animaledventures
